  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: When the last battle had been won, there was a problem to deal with. 
      Something had to be done about all the mana still in the environment.
    nextOption: 
  - startTime: 10
    showTime: 10
    description: The power of the sun could contain it, but at night, the SunSworn
      were powerless.
    nextOption: 
  - startTime: 20
    showTime: 10
    description: They had to find a solution that allowed them to contain the mana
      safely at all times.
    nextOption: 
  - startTime: 30
    showTime: 10
    description: It was decided that some of the technology created by magic use
      would be repurposed to create a seal that would work at all times.
